=== 參與國家及地區 ===
總共有92個代表團獲得資格（91個國家奧委會，以及來自俄羅斯的代表團將在奧運會旗下參賽）並都預計參加。原為95个代表团有资格参加，但由于来自开曼群岛、多米尼加和秘鲁的代表团将配额归还给[[国际滑雪联合会|国际滑雪联合会]]，因此无法参加<ref>{{cite web|url=https://data.fis-ski.com/media/olympic-games/2018/english-qs/owg-pyeongchang-2018-qualification-system-alpine-skiing.pdf|title=Qualification Systems for XXII Olympic Winter Games, PyeongChang 2018 Alpine skiing|date=2017-08-16|publisher=[[International_Ski_Federation|FIS]]|access-date=2018-01-20|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171209043920/https://data.fis-ski.com/media/olympic-games/2018/english-qs/owg-pyeongchang-2018-qualification-system-alpine-skiing.pdf|archive-date=2017-12-09}}</ref>。

[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鲜民主主义人民共和国]]（朝鮮）兩名花式滑冰運動員獲得參賽資格，若朝鮮決定參賽將被允許穿越[[朝韩非军事区|非軍事區]]入境韓國。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/winter-olympics/39969809|title=Pyeongchang 2018: Athletes to travel through demilitarised zone|date=2017-05-18|accessdate=2017-06-08|publisher=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|archive-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107022317/http://www.bbc.com/sport/winter-olympics/39969809|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1055988/north-korean-skaters-qualify-for-pyeongchang-2018|title=North Korean skaters qualify for Pyeongchang 2018|work=insidethegames.biz|publisher=Dunsar Media Company Limited|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210171827/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1055988/north-korean-skaters-qualify-for-pyeongchang-2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>朝鮮同意與韓國進行談判，派遣有資格的運動員參加冬季奧運會<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/08/world/asia/north-korea-south-olympics-border-talks.html|title=North Korea to Send Athletes to Olympics in South Korea Breakthrough|last=Sang-Hun|first=Choe|work=The New York Times|date=2018-01-08|accessdate=2018-01-09|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209200238/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/08/world/asia/north-korea-south-olympics-border-talks.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於俄羅斯在2016年被指出[[俄羅斯體育禁藥|國家支持使用禁藥]]，因此俄羅斯隊地位不明，存在整隊無緣參賽或只能[[獨立奧林匹克運動員|中立身分參賽]]或部分禁賽風險。<ref>{{cite news|title=With one year until 2018 Winter Games, Russia's status murky|url=http://www.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/18647088/with-one-year-2018-winter-games-pyeongchang-russia-status-murky-wake-doping-scandal|accessdate=|agency=|date=2017-02-09|archive-date=2018-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180228004357/http://www.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/18647088/with-one-year-2018-winter-games-pyeongchang-russia-status-murky-wake-doping-scandal|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]]決定禁止[[俄罗斯联邦|俄罗斯联邦]]作为国家参加，但表示俄罗斯运动员个人可以用“[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员|来自俄罗斯的奥林匹克运动员]]”的身份参加比赛<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/russia-olympic-20171205/4150579.html |title=国际奥委会禁止俄罗斯参加平昌冬奥会但允许俄运动员个人参赛 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2017-12-06 |accessdate=2017-12-06 |archive-date=2017-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205221608/https://www.voachinese.com/a/russia-olympic-20171205/4150579.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[普京|普京]]在12月6日表示，俄羅斯政府不會“阻止”任何運動員作為“個人”參加奧運會，但也有來自其他政治家的呼籲抵制不要參賽。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.sport-express.ru/olympics/pyeongchang2018/news/vladimir-putin-rossiya-ne-budet-prepyatstvovat-otpravke-sportsmenov-na-olimpiadu-v-neytralnom-statuse-1345146/ |title=Владимир Путин: "Никакой блокады Олимпиады не будет". ОЛИМПИАДА - Пхенчхан-2018. СПОРТ-ЭКСПРЕСС |trans-title= |publisher=Sport-express.ru |date= |accessdate=2017-12-06 |language=ru |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912175201/https://www.sport-express.ru/olympics/pyeongchang2018/news/vladimir-putin-nikakoy-blokady-olimpiady-ne-budet-1345146/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/russian/news-42250840 |title=Путин: Россия не будет объявлять "никакой блокады" Олимпиады - BBC Русская служба |trans-title= |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2017-12-06 |language=ru |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714083255/https://www.bbc.com/russian/news-42250840 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.interfax.ru/sport/590596 |title=Жириновский предложил отказаться от участия в Олимпиаде-2018 |trans-title= |publisher=Interfax.ru |date= |accessdate=2017-12-06 |language=ru |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231011733/http://www.interfax.ru/sport/590596 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/12/06/sport/russia-doping-2018-winter-olympics-vladimir-putin-pyeongchang/index.html|title=Vladimir Putin won't tell Russian athletes to boycott Winter Olympics|date=2017-12-06|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209193804/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/12/06/sport/russia-doping-2018-winter-olympics-vladimir-putin-pyeongchang/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[厄瓜多|厄瓜多]]、[[厄利垂亞|厄利垂亞]]、[[科索沃|科索沃]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]和[[新加坡|新加坡]]，都是首次參加冬季奧運。

