== 奖牌榜 ==
{{Main|2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会奖牌榜}}
{{:2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会奖牌榜}}

== 宣傳 ==
=== 奖牌 ===
[[File:Gold_medal_of_the_2018_Winter_Olympics_in_in_Pyeongchang.jpg|thumb]]
奖牌设计体现韩国传统和文化，重量从金牌的586克到铜牌的493克不等。正面是奥林匹克五环和取材于树干的对角线，象征着运动员的决心。反面是大项、小项和平昌2018标志。共有259套奖牌被铸造。整套奖牌是韩国设计师李苏佑的作品，他将韩国字母和韩国文化的基础[[谚文|谚文]]融汇到他们的设计中，通过一系列的辅音象征着全世界运动员的付出，他们聚在一起，一齐参赛。缎带利用韩国传统织物制造，浅蓝绿色间浅红色相间，也采用了谚文字母的绣花<ref name="ReferenceA">{{Cite web |url=https://www.olympic.org/pyeongchang-2018-medals |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2018-02-15 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119133346/https://www.olympic.org/pyeongchang-2018-medals |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 品牌 ===
赛会标志于2013年5月3日公布，为[[韩文|韩文]]字母p[[ㅍ|ㅍ]]和ch[[ㅊ|ㅊ]]，是主办城市平昌的出首音。此外，左侧的符号据称代表着{{le|韩国哲学|Korean philosophy}}中的“天地人合一”（{{lang-ko|천지인}}），右侧符号是[[冰晶|冰晶]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/pyeongchang-2018-launches-official-emblem|title=PyeongChang 2018 Launches Official Emblem|website=olympic.org|publisher=International Olympic Committee|accessdate=2016-08-12|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818103438/https://www.olympic.org/news/pyeongchang-2018-launches-official-emblem|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在所有官方文件中，主办城市平昌被写成[[驼峰式大小写|驼峰式大小写]]“PyeongChang”，而不是“Pyeongchang”，避免和名称类似的朝鲜首都[[平壤|平壤]]混淆<ref name=notpyongyang>{{cite news|title=Olympics: 2018 Winter Olympics … not in Pyongyang|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/olympics-2018-winter-olympics-not-in-pyongyang/|accessdate=2016-01-26|agency=Agence France-Presse|work=The Manila Bulletin|date=2016-01-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131130527/http://www.mb.com.ph/olympics-2018-winter-olympics-not-in-pyongyang/|archivedate=2016-01-31}}</ref>。

2017年1月，15个大项的24小项的官方[[象形符号|象形符号]]公布，灵感源于[[谚文|谚文]]字母<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/bbs/press/image/view?menuId=255&bbsId=28&searchOpt=&searchTxt=&pageNo=3&sortSeCd=3&cnId=45589&rows=36&langSeCd=en|title=PyeongChang 2018 Pictograms|date=2017-01-25|accessdate=2017-05-30|website=The PyeongChang 2018 Olympic and Paralympic Winter Games|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912175157/https://www.olympic.org/pyeongchang-2018|archive-date=2019-09-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 吉祥物 ===
{{main|Soohorang和Bandabi}}
[[File:KoreaNet_Honorary_Reporters_20161024_16_(30230802800).jpg|thumb]]
官方吉祥物2016年6月2日公布，Soohorang是[[孟加拉白虎|白虎]]，Bandabi是[[亚洲黑熊|亚洲黑熊]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1038038/tiger-and-bear-mascots-unveiled-for-pyeongchang-2018-winter-olympics-and-paralympics|title=Tiger and bear mascots unveiled for Pyeongchang 2018 Winter Olympics and Paralympics|date=2016-06-02|work=insidethegames.biz|publisher=Dunsar Media Company Limited|accessdate=2017-11-16|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117002729/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1038038/tiger-and-bear-mascots-unveiled-for-pyeongchang-2018-winter-olympics-and-paralympics|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/about-the-games|title=Introduction {{!}} PyeongChang 2018|last=pyeongchang2018|access-date=2018-02-06|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206154849/https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/about-the-games|archive-date=2018-02-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 游戏 ===
2017年6月，[[育碧|育碧]]的游戏作品《[[極限巔峰|極限巔峰]]》推出《奥林匹克之路》的可下载内容，新增和本届冬奥会有关的游戏模式和内容<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/10/12/steep-hits-the-olympics-with-new-expansion|title=Steep Hits the Olympics With New Expansion|last=Holt|first=Christian|date=2017-10-12|website=IGN|language=en-US|access-date=2018-01-23|archive-date=2018-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123141720/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/10/12/steep-hits-the-olympics-with-new-expansion|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/e3/2017/6/12/15786828/steep-road-to-winter-olympics-trailer-ubisoft-e3-2017|title=Steep’s first expansion is all about the Winter Olympics|last=Frank|first=Allegra|date=2017-06-12|website=Polygon|access-date=2018-01-23|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209193213/https://www.polygon.com/e3/2017/6/12/15786828/steep-road-to-winter-olympics-trailer-ubisoft-e3-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此之外，育碧亦取代[[世嘉|世嘉]]成為了本屆奧運會遊戲贊助商。

2017年11月，国际奥委会宣布支持并赞助在奥运会前夕举办的[[IEM英特爾極限高手盃|IEM英特爾極限高手盃]]《[[星际争霸II：自由之翼|星际争霸II：自由之翼]]》比赛，这被认为国际奥委会有意支持[[电子竞技|电子竞技]]加入[[奥运会表演项目|奥运会表演项目]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/e-sports-gets-closer-to-being-part-of-the-olympics-games-2017-10|title=E-sports just got closer to being part of the Olympics|work=Business Insider|access-date=2018-01-23|language=en|archive-date=2018-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201034147/http://www.businessinsider.com/e-sports-gets-closer-to-being-part-of-the-olympics-games-2017-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1057477/intel-announce-esports-tournament-to-take-place-in-pyeongchang-before-winter-olympics|title=Intel announce esports tournament to take place in Pyeongchang before Winter Olympics|work=Inside the Games|access-date=2018-01-23|archive-date=2018-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123190726/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1057477/intel-announce-esports-tournament-to-take-place-in-pyeongchang-before-winter-olympics|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2017/11/03/esports-pyeongchang-olympics-extreme-masters/ |title=Esports event in PyeongChang before Olympics supported by IOC |first=Nick |last=Zaccardi |date=2017-11-03 |accessdate=2017-11-05 |work=NBC Olympics |archive-date=2018-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130020301/http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2017/11/03/esports-pyeongchang-olympics-extreme-masters/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

最终，加拿大选手{{le|斯嘉丽 (星际争霸II玩家)|Scarlett (StarCraft II player)|莎拉·“斯嘉丽”·霍斯廷}}赢得比赛，她的胜利标志着北美职业玩家第二次在韩国举办的《星际争霸II》锦标赛上获胜，她也是第一位赢得大型锦标赛的女性<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/22358896/scarlett-becomes-first-woman-win-major-starcraft-ii-tournament |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2018-02-09 |archive-date=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208085609/http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/22358896/scarlett-becomes-first-woman-win-major-starcraft-ii-tournament |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://compete.kotaku.com/scarletts-starcraft-ii-victory-shows-how-esports-could-1822809807 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2018-02-09 |archive-date=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208033729/https://compete.kotaku.com/scarletts-starcraft-ii-victory-shows-how-esports-could-1822809807 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

