== 相關問題 ==
{{main|2018年冬季奧林匹克運動會相關問題}}
=== 半岛局势问题 ===
{{main|朝鲜半岛南北关系|2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会朝鲜代表团}}
本届冬奥会前夕，[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鲜]]加紧[[2017年朝鲜核试验|核试验]]、频繁试射[[导弹|导弹]]。外界普遍担忧本届冬奥会的安全性。

2017年9月20日，韩国总统[[文在寅|文在寅]]承诺会确保奥运会安全<ref>{{cite web|title=South Korea's Moon says pushing to guarantee safety at Pyeongchang Olympics|website=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2017-09-20|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-missiles-southkorea-olympi/south-koreas-moon-says-pushing-to-guarantee-safety-at-pyeongchang-olympics-idUSKCN1BU2YE|accessdate=2018-02-09|archive-date=2017-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923001951/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-missiles-southkorea-olympi/south-koreas-moon-says-pushing-to-guarantee-safety-at-pyeongchang-olympics-idUSKCN1BU2YE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，法国青年事务与体育部长[[劳拉·弗莱塞尔-科洛维奇|劳拉·弗莱塞尔-科洛维奇]]表示如果该国代表团的安全无法得到保障，将退出本届奥运<ref>{{cite web|title=France to skip 2018 Winter Games if security not assured|website=Reuters|date=2017-09-22|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-olympics-2018/olympics-france-to-skip-2018-winter-games-if-security-risk-too-great-idUKKCN1BW2NK|accessdate=2018-02-09|archive-date=2017-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922194329/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-olympics-2018/olympics-france-to-skip-2018-winter-games-if-security-risk-too-great-idUKKCN1BW2NK|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，一天后，澳大利亚和德国也表达类似的担忧，也表示会退出奥运会。后法国重申不会退出<ref>{{cite web|title=Olympics: North Korea triggers 2018 Winter Olympics security scare|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2017-09-23|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/sport/olympics-france-to-skip-2018-winter-games-if-security-risk-too-great-in-south-korea|accessdate=2018-02-09|archive-date=2017-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923020033/http://www.straitstimes.com/sport/olympics-france-to-skip-2018-winter-games-if-security-risk-too-great-in-south-korea|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年12月初，[[美国常驻联合国代表列表|美国常驻联合国代表]][[妮基·黑利|妮基·黑利]]称美国是否会参加本届冬奥会已成了“公开的疑问”，而这是因为担忧地区安全问题<ref>{{cite web|title=US ambassador to UN says it's an 'open question' whether U.S. athletes will participate in Winter Olympics over safety concerns|publisher=Business Insider|date=2017-12-07|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/olympics-us-south-korea-trump-nikki-haley-2017-12|accessdate=2018-02-09|archive-date=2017-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231103350/http://www.businessinsider.com/olympics-us-south-korea-trump-nikki-haley-2017-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但几天后白宫新闻秘书[[莎拉·桑德斯|莎拉·桑德斯]]表示美国“打算参赛”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://thehill.com/homenews/administration/363805-white-house-leaves-open-possibility-us-athletes-wont-participate-in|title=White House walks back remarks that US athletes might not participate in 2018 Olympics|last=Mitchell|first=Ellen|publisher=''The Hill''|date=2017-12-07|accessdate=2018-01-04|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103061146/http://thehill.com/homenews/administration/363805-white-house-leaves-open-possibility-us-athletes-wont-participate-in|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

随着朝鲜宣布参加本届冬奥会，[[唐纳德·特朗普|特朗普]]政府曾有讨论过抵制本届冬奥会<ref name="nyti_U.S.">{{Cite web | title = U.S. Skating Officials Brush Aside Talk of Boycotting Olympics | last = Longman | first = Jeré | work = The New York Times | date = 2018-01-03 | accessdate = 2018-01-06 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/03/sports/olympics/north-korea-olympics.html | archive-date = 2018-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180209201941/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/03/sports/olympics/north-korea-olympics.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但最终副总统[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]携妻子出席了本届冬奥会开幕式<ref name="pence">{{cite news|url=https://apnews.com/88d51e1604d6449693b0a64ce1bf70ef|title=Pence to lead US delegation to Olympics|work=Associated Press|date=2018-01-10|accessdate=2018-01-10|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922162511/https://apnews.com/88d51e1604d6449693b0a64ce1bf70ef|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年1月1日，金正恩发表新年演讲，提出在朝鲜参与本届冬奥会期间于[[首尔|首尔]]进行会谈<ref>{{cite news |title=Kim Jong Un highlights his ‘nuclear button,’ offers Olympic talks |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/north-korea/kim-says-north-korea-s-nuclear-weapons-will-prevent-war-n833781 |work=NBC News |date=2018-01-02 |accessdate=2018-02-07 |archive-date=2018-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207001019/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/north-korea/kim-says-north-korea-s-nuclear-weapons-will-prevent-war-n833781 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月18日，朝韩两国两年来首次进行高级会谈，共同宣布组建{{le|朝韩女子冰球联队|Korea women's national ice hockey team}}，并在[[2018年冬季奧林匹克運動會開幕式|开幕式]]手持[[统一旗|半岛旗]]进场<ref name="bbc-nkunified">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-42721417|title=Koreas to carry single flag at Olympics|date=2018|work=BBC News|access-date=2018-02-07|language=|archive-date=2018-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201104744/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-42721417|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pyolympics">{{cite news |title=‘The Pyongyang Olympics’ - Backlash in South Korea over plans to march with North at Winter Olympics |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/01/19/pyongyang-olympics-backlash-south-korea-plans-march-north/ |work=The Telegraph |date=2018-01-19 |accessdate=2018-02-07 |archive-date=2018-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207122848/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/01/19/pyongyang-olympics-backlash-south-korea-plans-march-north/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。惟部分韩国民众极力反对这一举措，他们认为政府正试图利用本届冬奥会传播亲朝鲜情绪，冰球联队不会如愿以偿<ref>{{cite news |title=South Korean protesters object to Olympic Games deal with North Korea |url=http://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-south-korea-olympics-protest-20180122-story.html |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2018-01-18 |accessdate=2018-02-08 |archive-date=2018-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207180003/http://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-south-korea-olympics-protest-20180122-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一同时，一部名为《平昌遗憾》（{{lang-ko|평창유감}}）的[[曲艺|说唱]]视频在韩国网络上流传，称赛事成了“[[平壤|平壤]]奥运会”<ref name="boybugs">{{cite news |title=Rap video frosty welcome for 2018 Winter Olympic Games |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-trending-42917511 |work=BBC News |date=2018-02-02 |accessdate=2018-02-07 |archive-date=2018-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209223712/http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-trending-42917511 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

日本外务大臣[[河野太郎|河野太郎]]甚至警告称，韩国不应该对朝鲜的“魅力攻势”疲软，轻易放松国家的压力<ref name="bbc-nkunified" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://time.com/5112104/north-south-korea-olympic-protests-moranbong/|title=Korean Olympic Cooperation Provokes Protests in Seoul|website=Time|language=|access-date=2018-02-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209200556/http://time.com/5112104/north-south-korea-olympic-protests-moranbong/|archivedate=2018-02-09}}</ref>。

[[韩国总统|韩国总统]][[文在寅|文在寅]]在开幕式上和朝鲜领导人[[金正恩|金正恩]]的妹妹[[金与正|金与正]]握手。这是自[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]以来[[金日成家族|金日成家族]]成员首次造访韩国<ref name="theg_USvi">{{cite web | title = US vice-president skips Olympics dinner in snub to North Korea officials | last = Haas | first = Benjamin | work = the Guardian | date = 2018-02-09 | accessdate = 2018-02-09 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/feb/09/kim-jong-uns-sister-arrives-in-south-korea-for-winter-olympics | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180209161430/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/feb/09/kim-jong-uns-sister-arrives-in-south-korea-for-winter-olympics | archivedate = 2018-02-09 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2018/02/olympics-opening-ceremony/552722/|title=North Korea's Undeserved Olympic Glory|last=Friedman|first=Uri|work=The Atlantic|access-date=2018-02-10|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180210013233/https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2018/02/olympics-opening-ceremony/552722/|archivedate=2018-02-10}}</ref>。

相反，[[美国副总统|美国副总统]][[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]在平昌会见了在朝鲜遭拘禁的[[奥托·瓦姆比尔|奥托·瓦姆比尔]]的父亲弗雷德·瓦姆比尔和[[脱北者|脱北者]]群体<ref>{{cite news|title=As North Koreans arrive at Olympics, Pence points to defectors to counter regime|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2018/02/09/politics/pence-south-korea-olympics/index.html|first=Elise|last=Labott|date=2018-02-09|accessdate=2018-02-17|work=CNN|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180217005258/https://edition.cnn.com/2018/02/09/politics/pence-south-korea-olympics/index.html|archivedate=2018-02-17}}</ref>。这使得朝鲜在最后时刻取消了和彭斯的会面<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.stuff.co.nz/world/americas/101642274/us-says-north-korea-cancelled-planned-meeting-with-us-vp-mike-pence |title= US says North Korea cancelled planned meeting with US VP Mike Pence |publisher= Stuff (Fairfax) |date= 2018-02-21 |accessdate= 2018-05-01 |archive-date= 2020-10-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201002145801/https://www.stuff.co.nz/world/americas/101642274/us-says-north-korea-cancelled-planned-meeting-with-us-vp-mike-pence |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

闭幕式上，朝鲜派出[[金英哲|金英哲]]将军作为代表。而他的出现受到韩国保守派的反对，称他在[[天安号沉没事件|天安号沉没事件]]有着重大责任，韩国统一部表示“指出事件负责人有局限性”。尽管受到制裁，韩国还是没有限制他在韩国进行访问活动<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-43169604|title=North Korea's controversial Olympics delegate|date=2018-02-23|work=BBC News|access-date=2018-03-13|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907234332/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-43169604|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/22/world/asia/north-korea-south-olympics.html|title=Former Spymaster to Lead North Korea’s Olympic Ceremony Delegation|last=Sang-Hun|first=Choe|date=2018-02-22|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-03-13|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103234332/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/22/world/asia/north-korea-south-olympics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 俄羅斯禁藥醜聞 ===
[[File:Olympic_Athlete_from_Russia_logo_2018.svg|thumb]]
{{main|俄罗斯体育禁药|2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯代表团|2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯代表团#禁药丑闻|2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员}}
2017年12月5日，国际奥委会宣布立即禁止俄罗斯奥委会参加2018年冬奥会。此前没有违反禁药规定且尿检历史一直良好的运动员可以在[[奥运五环|奥运五环旗]]下以“俄罗斯奥运运动员”身份参赛<ref name=":2" />。依照法令条款，俄罗斯政府官员被禁止出席奥运会，国旗和国歌都不能出现，改用奥林匹克旗和[[奥林匹克圣歌|奥林匹克圣歌]]。2017年12月20日，奥委会提议代表团制服使用替代标志（见右方）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-s-olympic-athlete-from-russia-implementation-group-releases-guidelines-for-uniforms-accessories-and-equipment|title=IOC's OAR implementation group releases guidelines for uniforms accessories and equipment's|date=2017-12-20|work=olympic.org|accessdate=2018-02-09|archive-date=2018-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323222145/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-s-olympic-athlete-from-russia-implementation-group-releases-guidelines-for-uniforms-accessories-and-equipment|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国际奥委会主席[[托马斯·巴赫|托马斯·巴赫]]表示：“在遵循正当程序后，国际奥委会对这一系统性的操纵行为进行了按比例的制裁，同时保护清白运动员<ref>{{cite web | url=https://themoscowtimes.com/news/ioc-bars-russian-athletes-and-officials-from-winter-olympic-games-59818 | title=IOC Bars Russian Athletes and Officials From Winter Olympic Games | work=The Moscow Times | date=2017-12-05 | accessdate=2017-12-05 | archive-date=2018-02-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227221154/https://themoscowtimes.com/news/ioc-bars-russian-athletes-and-officials-from-winter-olympic-games-59818 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

到2018年1月，奥委会按照{{le|奥斯瓦尔德委员会|Oswald Commission}}制裁了[[索契冬奥会|索契冬奥会]]的43名俄罗斯运动员，禁止他们参加2018年及日后的奥运会。除了其中一名运动员，所有人就他们的禁令上诉至[[国际体育仲裁院|国际体育仲裁院]]。仲裁院推翻了对28名运动员的制裁，恢复他们在索契获得的奖牌和成绩，但确认有足够的证据维持对11名运动员的制裁。国际奥委会在声明表示：“仲裁院决定结果并不意味着28名运动员将被邀请参加奥运会，不被制裁不会自动获得邀请特权”，“该案可能会对未来的反禁药运动产生严重影响。”国际奥委会认为，值得注意的是，国际体育仲裁院秘书长“坚称仲裁院的决定并不意味28名运动员是清白无辜的”，会考虑对仲裁结果提出上诉。仲裁院还决定应该仅禁止39名运动员参加2018年冬奥会。3名俄罗斯运动员仍然等待在2018年奥运会过后进行听证<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-statement-on-cas-decision|title=IOC Statement on CAS Decision|date=2018-02-01|publisher=International Olympic Committee|accessdate=2018-02-04|archive-date=2018-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180228002230/http://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-statement-on-cas-decision|dead-url=no}}</ref>。仲裁院决定公布后，28名赢得仲裁的运动员中，有15名（其中2名已退役，如今担任教练）申请奥运会邀请，但被国际奥委会拒绝<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.olympic.org/news/request-to-invite-15-athletes-and-coaches-to-pyeongchang-2018-for-the-olympic-athlete-from-russia-group-declined |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-02-09 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415141615/https://www.olympic.org/news/request-to-invite-15-athletes-and-coaches-to-pyeongchang-2018-for-the-olympic-athlete-from-russia-group-declined }}</ref>.。

俄罗斯曾考虑为本届奥运会派出500名备选的运动员，但经过考量立刻减掉了111名。剩下的运动员必须满足赛前条件，比如进一步的赛前测试和在分析储存样本。只有符合要求才能获邀参加奥运会。备选运动员均未被奥斯瓦尔德委员会制裁<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/reduced-pool-of-russian-athletes-and-officials-who-can-be-considered-for-invitation-to-pyeongchang-2018-determined|title=Reduced Pool of Russian Athletes and Officials Who Can Be Considered for Invitation to PyeongChang 2018 Determined|date=2018-01-25|publisher=International Olympic Committee|accessdate=2018-01-30|archive-date=2018-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121072858/https://www.olympic.org/news/reduced-pool-of-russian-athletes-and-officials-who-can-be-considered-for-invitation-to-pyeongchang-2018-determined|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受邀参加比赛的中立俄罗斯运动员人数最终确定为169人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/25/sports/olympics/russia-doping.html|title=Russia Is Barred From Winter Olympics. Russia Is Sending 169 Athletes to Winter Olympics|date=2018-01-25|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-02-04|archive-date=2018-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180325222518/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/25/sports/olympics/russia-doping.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此前，[[俄罗斯总统|俄罗斯总统]][[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]和其他官员表示，不允许他们的运动员拿着[[俄罗斯国旗|俄罗斯国旗]]参赛，对俄罗斯来说是奇耻大辱<ref>{{cite news |date=2017-10-19 |title=Putin says US pressured IOC to ban Russia from Winter Games |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/putin-says-us-pressured-ioc-ban-russia-winter-175151912--oly.html |work=Yahoo Sports |agency=Agence France-Presse |accessdate=2017-12-05 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206160927/https://sports.yahoo.com/putin-says-us-pressured-ioc-ban-russia-winter-175151912--oly.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，他的发言人后来说没有讨论过抵制<ref name=":2">{{cite news |last1=Ruiz |first1=Rebecca C. |last2=Panja |first2=Tariq |date=2017-12-05 |title=Russia Banned From Winter Olympics by I.O.C. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/05/sports/olympics/ioc-russia-winter-olympics.html |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate=2017-12-05 |archive-date=2019-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923090009/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/05/sports/olympics/ioc-russia-winter-olympics.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。国际奥委会决定宣布后，[[车臣共和国|车臣]][[车臣共和国首脑|首脑]][[拉姆赞·卡德罗夫|拉姆赞·卡德罗夫]]表示[[车臣人|车臣]]运动员不会以中立旗帜参赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.championat.com/other/news-2972433-kadyrov-ni-odin-chechenskij-sportsmen-ne-budet-vystupat-pod-nejtralnym-flagom.html|title=Кадыров: ни один чеченский спортсмен не будет выступать под нейтральным флагом|trans-title=|website=Championat.com|access-date=2017-12-06|language=|archive-date=2018-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227214904/https://www.championat.com/other/news-2972433-kadyrov-ni-odin-chechenskij-sportsmen-ne-budet-vystupat-pod-nejtralnym-flagom.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月6日，普京表示政府不会阻止运动员以个人名义参赛，但其他政客大声疾呼，要求抵制<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.interfax.ru/sport/590596 |title=Жириновский предложил отказаться от участия в Олимпиаде-2018 |trans-title= |publisher=Interfax.ru |date= |accessdate=2017-12-06 |language= |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231011733/http://www.interfax.ru/sport/590596 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。[[俄罗斯联邦共产党|俄罗斯联邦共产党]]主席[[根纳季·安德烈耶维奇·久加诺夫|根纳季·安德烈耶维奇·久加诺夫]]提议给观众送去苏联[[胜利旗|胜利旗]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mk.ru/politics/2018/01/30/zyuganov-predlozhil-otpravit-na-olimpiadu-bolelshhikov-so-znamenem-pobedy.html|title=Зюганов предложил отправить на Олимпиаду болельщиков со знаменем Победы|trans-title=|date=2018-01-30|work=mk.ru|accessdate=2018-02-05|language=|archive-date=2018-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205185139/http://www.mk.ru/politics/2018/01/30/zyuganov-predlozhil-otpravit-na-olimpiadu-bolelshhikov-so-znamenem-pobedy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|俄罗斯外交部长|Minister of Foreign Affairs (Russia)}}[[谢尔盖·维克托罗维奇·拉夫罗夫|谢尔盖·维克托罗维奇·拉夫罗夫]]表示美国“惧怕公平比赛”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://tass.com/politics/985069|title=US fears honest competition in energy, arms industry and sports, Lavrov warns|date=2018-01-15|publisher=TASS|accessdate=2018-01-18|archive-date=2018-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118181748/http://tass.com/politics/985069|dead-url=no}}</ref>，肯定普京认为美国在国际奥委会内部发挥影响力，“与禁药丑闻一唱一和”的立场<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-41934604|title=Putin: Doping allegations 'US plot against Russian election'|date=2017-11-09|work=bbc.com|accessdate=2018-01-18|language=|archive-date=2018-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207021806/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-41934604|dead-url=no}}</ref>。俄罗斯报纸《[[共青团真理报|共青团真理报]]》调查显示，86%的民众反对以中立旗帜参加奥运会<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.spb.kp.ru/daily/26772/3805611/|title=Опрос "КП": Стоит ли спортсменам из России ехать на Олимпиаду под нейтральным флагом|trans-title=|date=2017-12-20|work=kp.ru|accessdate=2018-02-04|language=|archive-date=2018-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205001038/https://www.spb.kp.ru/daily/26772/3805611/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

国际奥委会的拒绝遭到[[世界反运动禁药机构|世界反运动禁药机构]]俄罗斯禁药计划首席调查员杰克·罗伯特森（{{lang|en|Jack Robertson}}）的反对，表示国际奥委会发布“非惩罚性的惩罚意味在保护国际奥委会和俄罗斯的商业和政治利益的同时保存颜面。”他还强调俄罗斯告密者提供经验证据，“99%的国家级运动员都用了禁药”。他表示：“（世界反运动禁药机构）已经发现，俄罗斯运动员（达到）国家层面时，要么用禁药，要么完蛋，没有选择余地。”“目前我没有看到或听到任何情报，暗示国家资助的禁药计划已经消停”，他补充道<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nytimes.com/2017/12/27/opinion/2018-winter-olympics-russia.html|title=The 2018 Winter Olympics Are Already Tainted|work=The New York Times|date=2017-12-27|accessdate=2017-12-27|archive-date=2017-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227115758/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/27/opinion/2018-winter-olympics-russia.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。另据报道，俄罗斯官员密集游说美国政客，希望将大举报人[[格里戈里·羅德琴科夫|格雷戈里·罗德契科夫]]引渡回俄罗斯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1059507/ioc-accused-of-cowardice-for-failing-to-address-russian-retaliation-against-rodchenkov|title=IOC accused of cowardice for failing to address Russian retaliation against Rodchenkov|work=Inside the Games|date=2017-12-26|accessdate=2017-12-27|archive-date=2017-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226181140/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1059507/ioc-accused-of-cowardice-for-failing-to-address-russian-retaliation-against-rodchenkov|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

国际体育仲裁院推翻了28名俄罗斯运动的禁令，恢复他们的奖牌的决定，遭到包括国际奥委会主席托马斯·巴赫等官员的猛烈抨击，巴赫表示该决定“非常让人失望和意外”。格雷戈里·罗德契科夫的律师表示“仲裁院的决定允许使用禁药的运动员逃避惩罚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-olympics-ioc-chief-bach-disappointed-doping-bans-lifted/29017362.html|title=IOC Chief Disappointed By Court Lifting Doping Ban On Russians|work=rferl.org|date=2018-02-04|accessdate=2018-02-04|archive-date=2018-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180204145811/https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-olympics-ioc-chief-bach-disappointed-doping-bans-lifted/29017362.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”“（仲裁院的决定）为腐败的俄罗斯禁药体制，特别是普京带来不义之财。”，他补充道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2018/02/01/russia-olympic-doping-bans-lifted/|title=28 Russians have Olympic doping bans lifted|work=nbcsports.com|date=2018-02-01|accessdate=2018-02-04|archive-date=2018-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205000745/http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2018/02/01/russia-olympic-doping-bans-lifted/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 生態問題 ===
环保团体对建造[[旌善高山滑雪中心|旌善高山滑雪中心]]时砍伐{{le|加里王山|Gariwangsan}}森林的问题表示担忧。政府表示必须伐树才能建造符合奥运标准的斜坡，赛后将会恢复森林。由于森林包含树龄较长的稀有树种，团体对老树的生长持怀疑态度<ref>{{cite web |title=Olympics: Olympic organisers destroy 'sacred' South Korean forest to create ski run |publisher=The Guardian |date=2018-01-03 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2015/sep/16/olympic-organisers-destroy-sacred-south-korean-forest-to-create-ski-run |accessdate=2018-02-09 |archive-date=2020-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223200424/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2015/sep/16/olympic-organisers-destroy-sacred-south-korean-forest-to-create-ski-run |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 裁判判決引起不滿 ===
此次冬奥会裁判判罚问题引起了中國的不滿。其因是短道速滑的判罚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/zl/other/2018-02-25/zldoc-ifyrwsqh9873183.shtml|title=冬奥会多国裁判有压分内幕？|work=新浪体育|date=2018-02-25|accessdate=2018-03-06|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922162821/http://sports.sina.com.cn/zl/other/2018-02-25/zldoc-ifyrwsqh9873183.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在女子短道速滑接力赛中，中国队感到遭受不公正<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/223313705_823855|title=不平常的短道速滑女子3000米接力 无法可说 北京欢迎你！|work=搜狐体育|date=2018-02-20|accessdate=2018-03-06|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714085930/https://www.sohu.com/a/223313705_823855|dead-url=no}}</ref>的判罚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://k.sina.cn/article_6034621767_167b10547019003vkz.html|title=贿赂裁判，设“陷阱”，施压奥委会，韩国：我有100种抢金牌手段|work=新浪看点，每日点兵|date=2018-02-23|accessdate=2018-03-06|archive-date=2018-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180307151048/http://k.sina.cn/article_6034621767_167b10547019003vkz.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同样引起关注的是花样滑冰的判罚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/winter-olympics-2018/think-olympic-figure-skating-judges-are-biased-data-says-they-n844886|title=Think Olympic figure skating judges are biased? The data says they might be.|work=NBC news|date=2018-02-06|accessdate=2018-03-06|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109004153/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/winter-olympics-2018/think-olympic-figure-skating-judges-are-biased-data-says-they-n844886|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

